<p>User-level configuration lives in <code>~/.codex/config.toml</code>. You can also add project-scoped overrides in <code>.codex/config.toml</code> files. Codex loads project-scoped config files only when you trust the project.</p>
<p>For sandbox and approval keys (<code>approval_policy</code>, <code>sandbox_mode</code>, and <code>sandbox_workspace_write.*</code>), pair this reference with <a href="/codex/agent-approvals-security#sandbox-and-approvals">Sandbox and approvals</a>, <a href="/codex/agent-approvals-security#protected-paths-in-writable-roots">Protected paths in writable roots</a>, and <a href="/codex/agent-approvals-security#network-access">Network access</a>.</p>
