<p>You can find the latest JSON schema for <code>config.toml</code> <a href="/codex/config-schema.json">here</a>.</p>
<p>To get autocompletion and diagnostics when editing <code>config.toml</code> in VS Code or Cursor, you can install the <a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=tamasfe.even-better-toml">Even Better TOML</a> extension and add this line to the top of your <code>config.toml</code>:</p>
